casebody.head_matter:
Joseph Michael LADEAIROUS, petitioner,
v.
DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE.
No. 18-7980.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 15, 2019.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
Justice KAVANAUGH took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
